PLOT - Rick is an eccentric, elderly, alcoholic scientist who has moved in with the family 
of his veterinarian daughter, Beth. He spends most of his time taking his young grandson 
Morty (and later his granddaughter Summer) on dangerous, outlandish adventures throughout 
the cosmos and alternate universes. Compounded with Morty's already unstable family life, 
these events cause Morty much distress at home and school.
